import * as React from 'react';
  import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
  import Link from '@mui/material/Link';
  import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
  import KeyboardDoubleArrowRightIcon from '@mui/icons-material/KeyboardDoubleArrowRight';
  import Container from '@mui/material/Container';



  
  const Footer = () => {
    return(
  <Box sx={{ bgcolor: '#6ECCAF', p: 2 }}>
    <React.Fragment>
        <Container sx={{width:'100px',bgcolor:'red',dispaly:"flex",justifyContent:"row",marginRight:"0px"}} maxWidth="sm">



        <Grid container sx={{ color: "text.primary" }} >
        <Grid item xs={4} style={{color:"purple"}} sx={{marginLeft:"10px"}}>
        <KeyboardDoubleArrowRightIcon />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
        <Link href="/" variant="body2" underline="hover" sx={{color:"purple"}}>
                                     Home
                                      </Link>
         </Grid>
        </Grid>
       



        <Grid container sx={{ color: "text.primary" }}>
        <Grid item xs={4} style={{color:"purple"}}>
        <KeyboardDoubleArrowRightIcon />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
        <Link href="/aboutus" variant="body2" underline="hover" sx={{color:"purple"}}>
                                     About us
         </Link>
         </Grid>
         </Grid>



         
        <Grid container sx={{ color: "text.primary" }}>
        <Grid item xs={4} style={{color:"purple"}}>
        <KeyboardDoubleArrowRightIcon />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
        <Link href="/discover" variant="body2" underline="hover" sx={{color:"purple"}}>
                                     Discover
         </Link>
         </Grid>
         </Grid>




         <Grid container sx={{ color: "text.primary"}}>
        <Grid item xs={4} style={{color:"purple"}}>
        <KeyboardDoubleArrowRightIcon />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={3}>
        <Link href="/myaccount" variant="body2" underline="hover" sx={{color:"purple"}}>My account</Link>
         </Grid>
         </Grid>












         </Container>
         </React.Fragment>
         </Box >
   
        );}
export default Footer;
